          <p class="lead">Users can submit photos on the good the bad and the ugly freshwater management in your area or places you travel. To upload a photo click 'Submit' at the top of the page. You can view other photos on the map to see what is going on around NZ. All submissions are vetted before being made public. We have also created easy to use mobile Apps to instantly submit your photos.</p>
